wander around crime scenes.

110
00:08:44.568 --> 00:08:46.508
Sorry.

111
00:09:00.828 --> 00:09:02.848
Let's go over your story again.

112
00:09:02.848 --> 00:09:06.418
Your coworker Kusano-san was spending
a long time in the bathroom,

113
00:09:06.418 --> 00:09:08.688
so you went to check on him, correct?

114
00:09:09.408 --> 00:09:10.258
Yes.

115
00:09:10.838 --> 00:09:14.228
I left the restaurant and was
heading towards the bathroom

116
00:09:14.228 --> 00:09:18.078
