wearing a cap low over his eyes.

117
00:09:18.078 --> 00:09:21.698
The man headed towards the stairs.

118
00:09:22.998 --> 00:09:25.998
I ignored him and stopped
in front of the bathroom.

119
00:09:25.998 --> 00:09:29.918
I heard the hand drier
running inside the bathroom,

120
00:09:29.918 --> 00:09:33.928
