out right away and waited for a while,

121
00:09:34.968 --> 00:09:37.148
but he didn't come out.

122
00:09:37.908 --> 00:09:40.558
You didn't see anyone other than that man?

123
00:09:40.558 --> 00:09:43.078
No, I'm absolutely certain.

124
00:09:43.498 --> 00:09:46.308
That man who passed by
me must be the culprit.

125
00:09:47.148 --> 00:09:49.478
If only I'd gotten a better look at his face.

126
00:09:54.198 --> 00:09:58.988
Immediately after that, you heard
Yamanashi-san's voice and came here, right?

127
00:09:58.988 --> 00:10:03.588
Yeah. When we arrived,
Yamanashi-san was sitting here.

128
00:10:03.588 --> 00:10:07.368
I checked Kusano-san's pulse,
but he was already dead.

129
00:10:07.638 --> 00:10:11.628
Mori-san, you didn't see the
man in the cap, did you?

130
00:10:11.628 --> 00:10:15.128
