131
00:10:15.508 --> 00:10:17.658
What about you two, Ran-san and Conan-kun?

132
00:10:17.658 --> 00:10:20.588
I didn't run into anyone on the way here.

133
00:10:20.588 --> 00:10:24.188
I didn't see the man in the cap either.

134
00:10:24.188 --> 00:10:25.138
I see.

135
00:10:25.718 --> 00:10:30.268
We've started an emergency search for him
and are gathering information in the area.

136
00:10:30.268 --> 00:10:33.268
I hope we find some useful information.

137
00:10:33.268 --> 00:10:37.898
Since his wallet is still here, it looks
like the motive was a grudge and not theft.

138
00:10:38.178 --> 00:10:42.448
Most likely. That's how we're
investigating the case.

139
00:10:42.908 --> 00:10:48.628
