notice something was off sooner.

150
00:11:13.888 --> 00:11:17.688
In other words, didn't he do it so
the body would be discovered quickly?

151
00:11:18.158 --> 00:11:19.448
I see.

152
00:11:21.568 --> 00:11:24.818
If the culprit bothered
to do that, that means...

153
00:11:25.128 --> 00:11:26.538
That means...?

154
00:11:27.428 --> 00:11:28.808
What does it mean?

155
00:11:29.458 --> 00:11:31.528
If the culprit wanted to
hang around the bathroom,

156
00:11:31.528 --> 00:11:35.828
blending in with the customers at the various
restaurants on this floor would be the natural choice.

157
00:11:36.368 --> 00:11:40.838
The culprit could've used the confusion cause
by the discovery of Kusano-san's body to flee.

158
00:11:40.998 --> 00:11:46.218
None of the restaurants reported
a customer wearing a cap.

159
00:11:46.408 --> 00:11:51.718
So the man came here, attacked
Kusano-san, and left.

160
00:11:51.908 --> 00:11:55.798
And it doesn't make sense
since he couldn't have known

161
00:11:55.798 --> 00:11:57.228
when Kusano-san would go to the bathroom.

162
00:11:58.058 --> 00:12:00.858
You don't know what you're
talking about, kid.

163
00:12:01.078 --> 00:12:03.738
No, he's right. It doesn't make sense.

164
00:12:03.738 --> 00:12:07.428
