166
00:12:12.388 --> 00:12:17.178
For the time being, we'll have to keep
all manner of possibilities in mind.

167
00:12:18.918 --> 00:12:21.198
Hey, mister forensics officer.

168
00:12:21.998 --> 00:12:25.228
Did you retrieve the belongings
