grabbed it when he woke up.

227
00:16:22.158 --> 00:16:23.198
What?

228
00:16:24.648 --> 00:16:26.588
What are you talking about?

229
00:16:26.588 --> 00:16:28.788
That's just speculation.

230
00:16:28.788 --> 00:16:29.788
This is nonsense.

231
00:16:29.968 --> 00:16:31.968
Then allow me to confirm something.

232
00:16:31.968 --> 00:16:37.308
When you opened the bathroom door, you were
shocked to see Kusano-san on the floor.

233
00:16:37.308 --> 00:16:39.068
Then you shouted for help.

234
00:16:39.798 --> 00:16:43.348
In other words, you haven't set
foot inside the bathroom, correct?

235
00:16:43.568 --> 00:16:44.588
That's right.

236
00:16:44.588 --> 00:16:47.898
Maybe you just thought
my pant cuffs were wet.

237
00:16:48.408 --> 00:16:50.518
Look. They're not wet.

238
00:16:50.698 --> 00:16:55.128
Now that they're dry, I can't prove it.

239
00:16:55.908 --> 00:16:59.258
But what about your shirt sleeve button?

240
00:17:00.378 --> 00:17:02.308
Shirt sleeve button?

241
00:17:02.798 --> 00:17:06.038
When did you lose that?

242
00:17:06.258 --> 00:17:07.968
I...

243
00:17:08.688 --> 00:17:14.148
Forensics recovered the button
from the bathroom drain earlier.

244
00:17:15.468 --> 00:17:17.738
Hey, Mister Forensics Officer.

245
00:17:18.928 --> 00:17:22.268
Did you retrieve the belongings
that were in the drain?

246
00:17:22.268 --> 00:17:23.898
Of course.

247
00:17:24.478 --> 00:17:25.428
You mean this?

248
00:17:29.798 --> 00:17:34.928
Kusano-san's body was
covering the bathroom drain.

249
00:17:35.918 --> 00:17:41.198
If you haven't set foot inside the bathroom,
then how did your button get in there?

250
00:17:44.658 --> 00:17:49.938
Yes, because that button came off
during your scuffle with Kusano-san.

251
00:17:50.698 --> 00:17:53.188
It proves you're the culprit.

252
00:17:57.078 --> 00:17:59.788
